reviews.review_text: Best AUD of the bunch thanks MOTB!! this set is brighter/louder/better than the other AUD version available
Althea If for no other reason, DL this for the soulful rendition of Althea. It's a highly listenable and crisp if not technically perfect AUD. Points made, I'm outta' here and back to the show.
Great Audience Recording MOTB Strikes Again! Great sound and 3-D stereo.

LOUD Only twice in my life have I experienced a volume of music loud enough to hurt my ears. This night was one of them! The Swing Auditorium was an old airplane hangar that rocked and rolled as long and solidly as any place on the planet. Ironically, an airplane crashed into it and all we have now are the memories and tapes. Praise God for the taping community.
